description: The Parcel 2013 feature contains tax parcel polygons for the 2013 property tax assessment at the County. This feature reflects tax parcel polygons as they existed from 1/1/2013 through 12/31/2013. Each parcel is uniquely identified with a Property Index Number (PIN).
